data.text:
We invite you to attend the 37th International RAIS Conference on Social Sciences and Humanities organized by the Research Association for Interdisciplinary Studies (RAIS) which will be held hybrid (on-site and online) at The Erdman Center, 20 Library Place, Princeton, NJ 08540, USA, on August 8-9, 2024.
